  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dbd \u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dab \u0dc3\u0dd9\u0db6\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dba\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0d85\u0db4\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dd3\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We have never seen Ranil visiting the wounded soldiers before",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Member of Parliament Mrs. Hirunika Premachandra says that although the Acting President recently visited the Army Hospital to visit the injured soldiers, he has not done such a thing before.",
        "Also, she mentioned that the attention of the Acting Prime Minister is focused on getting the attention of some political groups to free Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake, who is currently serving a prison sentence.",
        "She also said that if Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe becomes the President in the upcoming election to elect a President in the Parliament, it will become a factor that could turn the country into a lake of blood."
      ],
